Cocktail: Suffering Bastard
Flavor Profile: Sour, Bitter, Spicy
Glassware: Standard Glass
Ingredients:
- 30 ml Cognac or brandy 30 ml Gin 15 ml lime juice 2 Dashes Angostura Bitters Top up Ginger beer

Preparation:
Pour all ingredients into cocktail shaker except the ginger beer, shake well with ice. Pour unstrained into a Collins glass or in the original. S. Bastard mug and top up with ginger bee